In the strictest scientific terms, what I mean by &quot;spirits&quot; are whatever apparrently &quot;intellegent entities&quot; that are the source of the percieved voices.

We REALLY do not know WHO 0r what they are.  That they may be parallel world entities or &quot;spirits&quot; is the usual working hyposithesis, based on the tradition of such entities existing in our culture and evidence suggesting that they DO exist and generally correspond to our concept of them/

